uccess.</p>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.</span></p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This campaign aims to foster a culture of learning and aspiration, and encourage students to envision and pursue their own paths to success.</p>","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}}},"QID8":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"vignette3","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"  We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broad...","QuestionID":"QID8","QuestionJS":false,"QuestionText":"<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<br>\n<br>\nThis campaign aims to foster a culture of learning and aspiration, and encourage students to envision and pursue their own paths to success.</span><p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"></p>On the next page, you will see a set of 25 biographies. We will ask you to select a subset of these biographies that you believe would be of broad interest to students and are therefore ideal to feature in our campaign.<p dir=\"ltr\"></p>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launchin