What is 13 + 39?<br>","QuestionType":"TE","SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"Selector":"SL","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_2cbaXVDl66VOsAu","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID5","SecondaryAttribute":"Informed Consent You are being asked to complete a survey as part of a research study about human...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"consent","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"Informed Consent You are being asked to complete a survey as part of a research study about human...","QuestionID":"QID5","QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Informed Consent<\/b><\/div>\n<br>\nYou are being asked to complete a survey as part of a research study about human behavior and decision-making. Your participation in this study is entirely voluntary. If you elect to participate, you will be asked to select an advisory panel based on a pool of options. You will then be asked to answer a series of survey questions. Additional information will be provided to you during your study participation.<br>\n<br>\nThis survey should take about 2 minutes. You can withdraw from the study at any time. If you decide to withdraw from the survey, your data will be destroyed. We will not share or store any data beyond the use of this research project.<br>\n<br>\nWe will make every effort to keep all the information you tell us during the study strictly confidential, except as required by law. Worker IDs will be collected strictly on the basis of compensation. Your name and other identifying information will never be connected with the responses you provide so no one will ever be able to identify you in any publications that will result from this research. If you have questions, concerns, or complaints regarding your confidentiality or if you have any questions about your rights as a research participant, you should e-mail the researcher at josecerv@wharton.upenn.edu. If a member of the research team cannot be reached or you want to talk to someone other than those working on the study, you may contact the Office of Regulatory Affairs with any questions, concerns, or complaints at the University of Pennsylvania by calling (215) 898-2614.<br>\n<br>\nIf you agree to participate, please click the arrow to continue. Otherwise, you may close the browser or navigate away from the page.","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Informed Consent<\/b><\/div>\n<br>\nYou are being asked to complete a survey as part of a research study about human behavior and decision-making. Your participation in this study is entirely voluntary. If you elect to participate, you will be asked to select an advisory panel based on a pool of options. You will then be asked to answer a series of survey questions. Additional information will be provided to you during your study participation.<br>\n<br>\nThis survey should take about 3 minutes. You can withdraw from the study at any time. If you decide to withdraw from the survey, your data will be destroyed. We will not share or store any data beyond the use of this research project.<br>\n<br>\nWe will make every effort to keep all the information you tell us during the study strictly confidential, except as required by law. Worker IDs will be collected strictly on the basis of compensation. Your name and other identifying information will never be connected with the responses you provide so no one will ever be able to identify you in any publications that will result from this research. If you have questions, concerns, or complaints regarding your confidentiality or if you have any questions about your rights as a research participant, you should e-mail the researcher at josecerv@wharton.upenn.edu. If a member of the research team cannot be reached or you want to talk to someone other than those working on the study, you may contact the Office of Regulatory Affairs with any questions, concerns, or complaints at the University of Pennsylvania by calling (215) 898-2614.<br>\n<br>\nIf you agree to participate, please click the arrow to continue. Otherwise, you may close the browser or navigate away from the page.","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_2cbaXVDl66VOsAu","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID6","SecondaryAttribute":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"vignette","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","QuestionID":"QID6","QuestionJS":false,"QuestionText":"<p dir=\"ltr\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<\/p>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<p dir=\"ltr\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<\/p>","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_2cbaXVDl66VOsAu","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID7","SecondaryAttribute":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"vignette2","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","QuestionID":"QID7","QuestionJS":false,"QuestionText":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This campaign aims to foster a culture of learning and aspiration, and encourage students to envision and pursue their own paths to success.<\/p>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This campaign aims to foster a culture of learning and aspiration, and encourage students to envision and pursue their own paths to success.<\/p>","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_2cbaXVDl66VOsAu","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID8","SecondaryAttribute":"\u00a0 We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broad..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"vignette3","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"\u00a0 We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broad...","QuestionID":"QID8","QuestionJS":false,"QuestionText":"<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<br>\n<br>\nThis campaign aims to foster a culture of learning and aspiration, and encourage students to envision and pursue their own paths to success.<\/span><p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><\/p>On the next page, you will see a set of 25 biographies. We will ask you to select a subset of these biographies that you believe would be of broad interest to students and are therefore ideal to feature in our campaign.<p dir=\"ltr\"><\/p>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<br>\n<br>\nThis campaign aims to foster a culture of learning and aspiration, and encourage students to envision and pursue their own paths to success.<\/span><p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><\/p>On the next page, you will see a set of 25 biographies. We will ask you to select a subset of these biographies that you believe would be of broad interest to students and are therefore ideal to feature in our campaign.<p dir=\"ltr\"><\/p>","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_2cbaXVDl66VOsAu","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID9","SecondaryAttribute":"Thank you for your responses. We just have a few more questions.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"Q23","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"Thank you for your responses. We just have a few more questions.","QuestionID":"QID9","QuestionText":"Thank you for your responses. We just have a few more questions.<br>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Thank you for your selections. We just have a few more questions.<br>","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_2cbaXVDl66VOsAu","Element":"STAT","PrimaryAttribute":"Survey Statistics","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"MobileCompatible":true,"ID":"Survey Statistics"}}]}
