C:\Users\jcerv\Jose\diversity_feedback\revision-analysis\_r2_review\r2_manuscript_changes_v3.md:314:**Background.** The current Table 2 footnote on manuscript line 383 contains: "Study 1 is excluded because participants did not generate their own initial selections (the initial portfolio was stimulus-sampled), and Study 5 is excluded because its design varies the initial candidate pool's composition rather than holding it constant." But Table 2 itself INCLUDES Study 1 (line 365). The exclusion language belongs with a different analysis (the new zero-restriction pooled analysis described in response letter line 44), not Table 2.
